metadata.title: Rubbermaid Commercial Products ProSave Shelf-Storage Ingredient Bin With Scoop, 400-cup capacity, Plastic, White, Sliding Lid, Container with Wheels for Kitchen/Restaurant Food Organization
features: SUPERIOR MANEUVERABILITY: two fixed front castors and 2 swivel rear castors
INTEGRATED LID: clear sliding lid for one handed access and easy identification of ingredients
FOOD SAFTEY: internal scoop hanger to keep food from unwanted bacteria
DISHWASHER SAFE: all parts of the lids and scoops are commercial dishwasher safe
SPACE SACING: rectangular design improved space optimization
DIMENSIONS: Measures 13-1/8" W x 29-1/4" L x 28" H
description: The Rubbermaid Commercial ProSave Ingredient and Food Storage Mobile Bin is a bulk food storage container on wheels. With a slanted front, sliding opening, and 32-ounce scoop, these food storage containers makes it easy to transport ingredients. These bulk food storage containers feature 2 fixed front castors and 2 swivel rear castors that provide superior maneuverability. The mobile bin has a white bottom and clear lid for easy identification of ingredients.
